INSTALL
=======

Pegasus NoteTaker Linux drivers library
=======================================

Table of contents
=================

1. Introduction
2. Requirements
3. Installation

1. Introduction
===============
This INSTALL file contains the instructions to install the M210 drivers.

2. Requirements
===============
The requirements are stated in the README file. Please be sure every dependency is satisfied before installation (unless you know exactly what you are doing).

3. Installation
===============
As root:

- run './setup-drivers.sh USER' where USER is the target user for the installation
- run './setup-m210office.sh USER' where USER is the target user for the installation

If everything goes well, as USER:

- log off then log in to your session
- run 'm210office'
